    <div class="container py-5" style="background-color: transparent;">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4" style="color:green;letter-spacing: 0.4vh; font-size: 4vh;">Games Collection</h1>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4">
            <div class="col" style="margin-bottom: 3vh;">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                   
                    <div class="card-body" id="id1">
                        <h2 style="font-size: 3vh; color: #0d1117; font-weight: 500 ; letter-spacing: 0.3vh;">Budgeting Simulator</h2>
                        <p class="card-text" style="font-size: medium; color: #0d1117; font-weight: 400 ; letter-spacing: 0.3vh;">Objective: The goal of the game is to manage your finances by making smart, mindful decisions. If you manage to save wisely, you will earn additional money!<br>

                            Gameplay:<br>
                            
                            Player is given a starting budget.<br>
                            During the game, player must make decisions on how to allocate their money across different categories (e.g., essentials, savings, luxuries).
                            The key is to mindfully allocate your money. If you save properly, you'll get 100 finzos added to your account.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <div class="btn-group">
                                <a href="http://localhost:5000/confirmsecond"><button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">Play</button></a>
                              
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col" style="margin-top: 5vh;" >
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                   
                    <div class="card-body" id="id2">
                        <h2 style="font-size: 3vh; color: #0d1117; font-weight: 500 ; letter-spacing: 0.3vh;">Credit Score</h2>

                        <p class="card-text" style="font-size: medium; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400 ; letter-spacing: 0.3vh;">Objective: The goal is to make smart financial decisions to improve your credit score. Choosing the right actions will lead to rewards, while poor choices could cost you.<br>

                            Gameplay:<br>
                            
                            Players are presented with different financial scenarios that can impact their credit score (e.g., paying bills on time, taking out loans).<br>
                            Players must select the optimal financial action to improve or maintain their credit score.<br>
                            If the player makes the right choice and optimally manages their credit, 10 finzos will be added to their account.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <div class="btn-group">
                                <a href="http://localhost:5000/confirm"><button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">Play</button></a>
                               
                      
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
